From acef5858c5b0bedf8ba15497c2d95c45056bab92 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: kierandrewett <kieran@drewett.dev>
Date: Mon, 13 Jul 2026 14:48:03 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] gnoblin-panel: pin gnoblin to the top of the sidebar with a
 separator

Add "gnoblin" as the first entry in panel_order[] followed by a
"separator" pseudo-entry. get_panel_id_index() then sorts the gnoblin
row above the Wi-Fi/Network block (index 0), and header_func() draws a
horizontal separator above the following "wifi" row -- so the gnoblin
row sits at the very top, visually detached from the connectivity
section below it.

Previously "gnoblin" was absent from panel_order[] and fell back to
index 0, tying with "wifi" and getting no separator.
---
 shell/cc-panel-list.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/shell/cc-panel-list.c b/shell/cc-panel-list.c
index 2b59587..6e1726a 100644
--- a/shell/cc-panel-list.c
+++ b/shell/cc-panel-list.c
@@ -370,6 +370,10 @@ filter_func (GtkListBoxRow *row,
 
 static const gchar * const panel_order[] = {
   /* Main page */
+  "gnoblin",
+
+  "separator",
+
   "wifi",
   "network",
   "wwan",
-- 
2.53.0

